metadata_description: PS>Attack combines some of the best projects in the infosec powershell community into a self contained custom PowerShell console. Its designed to make it easy to use PowerShell offensively and to evade antivirus and Incident Response teams. It does this with in a couple of ways.
PSAttack contains over 100 commands for Privilege Escalation - Recon and Data Exfilitration
